  "1792660": {
    "name": "Runaway Animals",
    "steam_appid": 1792660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以故事为引导的游戏。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>难易度选择。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>单人游戏和至多4人的多人游戏。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>奖励系统。让你玩的越多，得到的新角色和皮肤就越多。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/54ffdb0c7ee508737160f6ba2ccd5db1.poster.avif?t=1729032700\" width=570 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/54ffdb0c7ee508737160f6ba2ccd5db1.webm?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/54ffdb0c7ee508737160f6ba2ccd5db1.mp4?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏参数可调节，提高个性化的体验和重玩性。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>短句交流功能。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>很多人在不同的地方看到了一个神秘的人带着一只猴子。这人一般会放走被关起来的动物。有时候这些动物逃跑了，跑到了它们不该在的地方。官方仍对这更让的身世和动机一无所知。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/9d3b872b1cd6e1fbc1c4db374573fda9.poster.avif?t=1729032700\" width=570 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/9d3b872b1cd6e1fbc1c4db374573fda9.webm?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/9d3b872b1cd6e1fbc1c4db374573fda9.mp4?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在第一章，你是暴君大酒店的一名低薪职员。你必须在不受控制的动物们乱跑时完成你所有的任务。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以利用周围的物件来帮你抵御野生动物的攻击。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/f7adb4ebd525405e9c1b064c27703aca.poster.avif?t=1729032700\" width=570 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/f7adb4ebd525405e9c1b064c27703aca.webm?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/f7adb4ebd525405e9c1b064c27703aca.mp4?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以使用强化道具来恢复生命，跑得更快，力量更强，并在短时间内隐身。你也可以把强化道具分给身边的玩家。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/1d8e3e96531385c82f5a29a89b2ca8ce.poster.avif?t=1729032700\" width=570 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/1d8e3e96531385c82f5a29a89b2ca8ce.webm?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792660/extras/1d8e3e96531385c82f5a29a89b2ca8ce.mp4?t=1729032700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你还有一个短句聊天菜单，在那里你可以把一些相关的关键词组合在一起。你可以把这些信息发给其他玩家。他们看到的是自己选择的语言。这样一来你甚至可以可以和不同语言的玩家交流。</li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 韩语, 简体中文, 德语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 法语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 日语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
